01:03:13,283.4444444444962 --> 01:03:14,278
Hello
<i>- Hola.</i>

1207
01:03:18,397 --> 01:03:20,453
Good afternoon
<i>Buenas tardes.</i>

1208
01:03:23,300 --> 01:03:25,469
I was working for a time…
<i>Cuando yo estaba trabajando,</i>

1209
01:03:25,670 --> 01:03:27,220
The landlord came
<i>vino el dueño.</i>

1210
