How'd he throw you out? police?
<i>¿Lo botó? ¿Cómo? ¿De qué manera?</i>

1214
01:03:37,347 --> 01:03:40,559.4615384615026
Yes, he brought the police, he's rich
<i>Sí. Trajo policía. Es que es de plata.</i>

1215
01:03:40,560.4615384615026 --> 01:03:42,904
he's got lots of money
<i>Tiene dinero, bastante.</i>

1216
01:03:42,920 --> 01:03:45,381.88888888899237
