<i>Quiere que yo abandone su terreno.</i>

1217
01:03:45,382.88888888899237 --> 01:03:46,412
to get out
<i>Dejarlo.</i>

1218
01:03:46,490 --> 01:03:47,761.25
Once it was already productive
<i>- ¿Y ya estaba produciendo?</i>

1219
01:03:47,762.25 --> 01:03:50,105.39622641494498
Yes, it was producing
<i>- Sí. Ya estaba produciendo</i>

1220
01:03:50,106.39622641494498 --> 01:03:53,498
wheat, corn, potato all that
<i>trigo, maíz, papas, habas, todo.</i>

1221
