I think we know each other
<i>Creo que ya nos conocemos </i>

1312
01:09:28,279.5555555555038 --> 01:09:29,128
pretty well now
<i>lo suficiente.</i>

1313
01:09:29,199 --> 01:09:31,376
Let me tell you something
<i>Puedo permitirme decirles algo.</i>

1314
01:09:31,377 --> 01:09:33,62.92307692300528
I look at you in the eyes, 
<i>Los miro a los ojos,</i>

1315
01:09:33,63.92307692300528 --> 01:09:35,638
Ernesto, and you, Alberto,
<i>a ti Ernesto y a ti Alberto.</i>

1316
01:09:35,639 --> 01:09:37,965.8571428572759
and I see great idealism 
<i>Y veo en ustedes un gran idealismo.</i>

1317
01:09:38,341 --> 01:09:40,571
and also many doubts
<i>Pero también muchas dudas.</i>

1318
01:09:40,644 --> 01:09:41,610.8125
That's why I'm glad
<i>Por eso, me alegra</i>

1319
01:09:41,611.8125 --> 01:09:43,078
you're going to San Pablo
<i>que vayan a San Pablo.</i>

1320
01:09:43,146 --> 01:09:44,116.60377358505502
I think you will find
<i>Me parece que ahí</i>

1321
01:09:44,117.60377358505502 --> 01:09:46,172
something important there
<i>van a encontrar algo importante.</i>

1322
01:09:46,173 --> 01:09:49,116
Important for you
<i>lmportante para ustedes.</i>

1323
