<i>- Un libro. - Un libro.</i>

1329
01:10:01,808.1538461539894 --> 01:10:04,633
- Eating good Lito. Ya?
<i>- Comés bien, Lito. ¿Eh?</i>

1330
01:10:04,634 --> 01:10:06,719.9090909091756
This is the great love of my life,
