It's my novel
<i>Es mi novela.</i>

1334
01:10:12,967 --> 01:10:15,238
"Latitudes of Silence"
<i>Latitudes del silencio.</i>

1335
01:10:16,005 --> 01:10:18,510
I hope you'll do me the honor of reading it
<i>Espero que me hagan el honor de leerla.</i>

1336
01:10:18,511 --> 01:10:20,276
- Of course. - Of course.
<i>- Claro. - Claro.</i>

1337
01:10:20,350 --> 01:10:22,287.2972972970456
The honor is ours
<i>- Es un honor. El honor es nuestro.</i>

1338
01:10:22,288.2972972970456 --> 01:10:24,262
You can give me your opinion in Ucayali
<i>- En el Uyacali, me dan su opinión.</i>

1339
01:10:24,263 --> 01:10:25,771.2941176472232
- Of course May I?
<i>- Con gusto, sí. ¿La puedo abrir?</i>

1340
01:10:25,772.2941176472232 --> 01:10:26,755
- Of course.
<i>- Sí.</i>

1341
01:10:26,756 --> 01:10:29,725
Who dares go first?
<i>¿Quién se anima a leerla primero?</i>

